1
00:00:19,580 --> 00:00:21,820
Mr. Shen, you have become
quite domineering lately.

2
00:00:22,180 --> 00:00:23,620
Things have been tense recently.

3
00:00:23,620 --> 00:00:24,939
You should stop your moves for now.

4
00:00:24,940 --> 00:00:27,340
Our engagement
has already been called off.

5
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:29,220
My matters

6
00:00:29,580 --> 00:00:31,060
are none of your concern.

7
00:00:35,140 --> 00:00:38,140
Just in time,
return it to its rightful owner.

8
00:01:17,140 --> 00:01:18,180
Just in time,

9
00:01:18,570 --> 00:01:20,020
return it to its rightful owner.

10
00:01:24,020 --> 00:01:25,060
Miss.

11
00:01:25,740 --> 00:01:26,459
Uncle Li.

12
00:01:26,460 --> 00:01:27,179
Miss.

13
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:28,619
Mr. Xu asked me to inform you

14
00:01:28,620 --> 00:01:30,060
that he wants to see Shen Gu.

15
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:37,879
=Echoes of Gang City=

16
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:43,080
=Episode 6=
(A Hidden Flutter at the Cuff)

17
00:01:50,020 --> 00:01:51,620
So formal.

18
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:55,500
I do not recall
any scheduled meetings today.

19
00:01:55,980 --> 00:01:57,540
I will go see Grandfather.

20
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,940
Do not take
yesterday's matter too seriously.

21
00:02:03,980 --> 00:02:04,739
Relax.

22
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:05,780
Just be yourself.

23
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:08,020
Thanks for the encouragement.

24
00:02:24,980 --> 00:02:26,140
Shen Gu,

25
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,660
during this time,

26
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,660
you have worked hard.

27
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:32,220
It is only right.

28
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:36,220
These two trees

29
00:02:36,580 --> 00:02:39,499
were planted by Zhaoming and me

30
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:41,300
the year we took Wanxin in.

31
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:47,420
You have raised Wanxin very well.

32
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:52,980
It is precisely
because she is so remarkable

33
00:02:54,100 --> 00:02:56,420
that it makes people uneasy.

34
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:03,779
I heard from Wanxin

35
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:07,100
that the marriage was her idea.

36
00:03:08,380 --> 00:03:10,020
I understand

37
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:12,100
her reasoning.

38
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:16,820
What matters now is what you think.

39
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:19,860
Between Wanxin and me,

40
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,620
there is no contract marriage,

41
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:23,420
nor any weighing of gains and losses.

42
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:28,500
I simply wish

43
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:30,020
to be the one who loves her.

44
00:03:37,540 --> 00:03:42,020
What if things do not go as you hope?

45
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:44,220
What if she
does not fall in love with you?

46
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:49,300
If she does not love me,

47
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:51,700
she is free to leave at any time.

48
00:03:52,100 --> 00:03:53,460
That is her choice.

49
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:04,420
Grandfather.

50
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:08,140
Wanxin.

51
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:20,220
This year's annual charity gala

52
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:24,940
will be entrusted to the two of you
to host on my behalf.

53
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:27,539
Grandfather,

54
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:30,260
this is the charity gala
you founded yourself.

55
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:32,899
Now that you have already...

56
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:35,020
I am getting old.

57
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:36,700
From now on,

58
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:40,580
I will gradually hand over

59
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:42,900
the company's affairs to you.

60
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:45,340
For Minghui,

61
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:48,020
this charity gala

62
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:51,020
was founded by my benefactor.

63
00:04:51,980 --> 00:04:53,740
After his passing,

64
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:56,140
I have continued to host it every year.

65
00:04:56,540 --> 00:04:57,820
It not only

66
00:04:58,220 --> 00:05:02,220
holds great significance for Minghui,

67
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,099
but to the outside world,

68
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:08,020
it is also a recognition
of our family's standing.

69
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:11,460
As Interim Chairwoman,

70
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:15,100
many around you
are still watching closely.

71
00:05:15,300 --> 00:05:17,619
So this charity gala

72
00:05:17,620 --> 00:05:19,460
must be hosted by you

73
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:21,500
in person.

74
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:24,620
Do not worry, Grandfather.

75
00:05:25,180 --> 00:05:26,460
I will make sure it is done well.

76
00:05:29,580 --> 00:05:31,340
I will fully support Wanxin.

77
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:43,020
Then this matter is entrusted
to the two of you.

78
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,820
The cooperation
between Minghui and Qingniao

79
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,679
has brought us major shareholders

80
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,120
a substantial profit.

81
00:05:54,540 --> 00:05:56,819
You sold all your shares.

82
00:05:56,820 --> 00:05:58,020
What a pity.

83
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:01,299
What is the point of profit?

84
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:03,060
Your old man is awake.

85
00:06:03,100 --> 00:06:04,660
Has he seen you?

86
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:17,040
(Letter of Intent for Cooperation)

87
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:24,179
Whether it is Minghui, Shen Gu,

88
00:06:24,180 --> 00:06:25,339
or Qingniao,

89
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:26,500
in the end,

90
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:28,420
none of them will get past me.

91
00:06:30,220 --> 00:06:32,139
How did Shen Gu manage to do it?

92
00:06:32,140 --> 00:06:33,339
The moment Xu Qianmo woke up,

93
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:33,979
he had Xu Wanxin

94
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:36,820
host such an important charity gala.

95
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:38,220
Watch your tone.

96
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:41,020
Is Mr. Xu someone
you can address so casually?

97
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:49,540
Being able to host it is one thing.

98
00:06:50,140 --> 00:06:52,860
Doing it well is another.

99
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:59,020
If I am not doing well,

100
00:06:59,700 --> 00:07:01,420
no one else will have it easy either.

101
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:04,100
Hao,

102
00:07:04,260 --> 00:07:06,860
this charity gala
is being held at my hotel.

103
00:07:06,980 --> 00:07:08,739
If things get too ugly,

104
00:07:08,740 --> 00:07:11,300
my father will
be even less willing to see me.

105
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:14,260
At least show some respect for me.

106
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:17,420
Be mindful of your words and actions.

107
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:19,420
Do not scare Uncle Xu.

108
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:24,260
I understand.

109
00:07:25,620 --> 00:07:27,500
All I want is to bring down
Xu Wanxin and Shen Gu.

110
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:50,640
(Utmost Brightness & Radiance
Charity Gala)

111
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:54,080
(Utmost Brightness & Radiance
Charity Gala)

112
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:18,040
(Minghui Group. Utmost Brightness
& Radiance Charity Gala)

113
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:26,400
(Fang Hongsheng)

114
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:38,699
(Shen Hao)

115
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:40,659
Congratulations, Mr. Zhaohui.

116
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,700
You have made a huge profit this time.

117
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:45,139
With Minghui and Qingniao partnering up,

118
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:48,819
you can just sit back at home
and count money from now on.

119
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:51,579
Not at all. This is all thanks
to my elder brother's efforts before.

120
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:52,339
The partnership

121
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:54,099
was also secured by him earlier.

122
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:55,620
This way, please.

123
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:57,939
Mr. Qian.

124
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:58,779
Mr. Qian.

125
00:08:58,780 --> 00:09:01,179
I heard Mr. Xu has already
regained consciousness.

126
00:09:01,180 --> 00:09:02,699
Will he make an appearance tonight?

127
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:05,620
As far as I know,
he has never missed one.

128
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:07,299
Well,

129
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:07,899
right now,

130
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:10,019
both the family and the company
are managed by Wanxin.

131
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:10,779
So tonight's auction

132
00:09:10,780 --> 00:09:12,299
will be attended by her

133
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:14,059
on behalf of my father.

134
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:15,320
(Charity Gala Execution Plan)

135
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:22,940
Xi,

136
00:09:23,140 --> 00:09:24,900
help me double check again

137
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:27,500
whether there are any

138
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:29,100
divorced couples,

139
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:30,899
former partners,

140
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:32,399
or business rivals on the seating list.

141
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:34,199
Instead of worrying about that,

142
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,839
you should worry about

143
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:38,360
Shen Tingyuan and his son
on the guest list.

144
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,440
I am actually concerned
they might target you.

145
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:45,639
Although they have already sold off

146
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:48,000
all their Minghui shares,

147
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:52,160
we may still have future collaborations.

148
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:54,720
If we do not invite them,

149
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,720
it would make us seem small-minded.

150
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,760
Mm.

151
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,240
Alright.

152
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,079
I will go over it again for you.

153
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,200
Mm.

154
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,720
This way, Mr. Shen.

155
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,560
Careful.

156
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:55,000
All set, Mr. Shen.

157
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,160
I have finished checking.

158
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,560
Your arrangements

159
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,640
have no issues at all.

160
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,960
Good.

161
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,720
I will leave it for now.

162
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:22,960
My girl has truly grown up.

163
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,399
Seeing you today,

164
00:11:24,400 --> 00:11:26,720
I feel even prouder than
when you first hosted a program.

165
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:34,000
I am still a little nervous.

166
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:36,200
No need to be nervous.

167
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:39,160
You look absolutely perfect today.

168
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:41,160
Alright,

169
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:43,599
I will go take
another look around for you,

170
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,040
so you do not have to worry.

171
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:45,839
Mm.

172
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:46,800
Love you.

173
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,799
Mr. Song, congratulations.

174
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:27,919
You have made quite a fortune this time.

175
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:30,159
The Minghui shares in your hands

176
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:32,480
are rising with the tide.

177
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,319
I am relying on my daughter.

178
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:36,520
She has a good eye for people.

179
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:40,399
This time Minghui managed
to break free from Shen Tingyuan.

180
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:43,640
Xu Wanxin and Shen Gu
do have some capability.

181
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:45,040
Right?

182
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:49,479
Make way.

183
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,800
Excuse me.

184
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:53,040
Mr. Shen is here.

185
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,920
Mr. Tingyuan.

186
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:00,320
Mr. Tingyuan.

187
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,400
Mr. Shen Hao.

188
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:05,799
Mr. Tingyuan,

189
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:07,719
your presence today

190
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,120
really shows great magnanimity.

191
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:12,399
Mr. Shen is truly broad-minded.

192
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:14,719
Young people these days
can be a bit rough in handling matters.

193
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:18,520
Having someone as experienced as Mr. Shen
here to steady things is excellent.

194
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:22,919
I came to see Wanxin as well,

195
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:26,560
to see how this charity gala
will turn out.

196
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,440
But

197
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:34,160
being able to purchase
Minghui's auction items

198
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:39,360
does not necessarily mean you can secure
a chance to work with Junlin Group.

199
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,679
So tell me,

200
00:13:58,680 --> 00:14:01,119
are we bidding today or not?

201
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,599
Shen Gu came back this time

202
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:05,599
to go against Shen Tingyuan
using the Xu family.

203
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,560
So it is best for us
not to get involved.

204
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:12,120
The Xu family might lose face this time.

205
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:16,239
Mom, with the way those uncles
gather information behind the scenes,

206
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:18,119
it is a pity they are not

207
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,840
in our TV station's newsroom.

208
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,839
Do not joke with your uncles.

209
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:23,759
When it comes to news,

210
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,560
they cannot compare with you.

211
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:26,699
That is true.

212
00:14:26,700 --> 00:14:28,599
After all, we deal with news,

213
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:30,000
not gossip.

214
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:32,919
This girl

215
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:34,439
really has a sharp tongue.

216
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,519
Ms. Song,

217
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:38,239
you cannot spoil a child like this forever.

218
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,679
Especially a girl.

219
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:43,720
She will suffer when she
marries into another family.

220
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:47,239
If she has to suffer,
then she will not marry.

221
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:49,799
My daughter has been cherished
by me since she was little.

222
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,799
She is closest to Wanxin.

223
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:55,000
Her stance is the stance
of our Song family.

224
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:58,040
Of course.

225
00:14:58,680 --> 00:14:59,999
Take care, uncles.

226
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,200
See you next time.

227
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,439
Do not call me Mom in public.

228
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:06,719
There are so many people here.
Or I will cut your cards.

229
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:08,720
Got it, Mommy.

230
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:11,120
Madam Song.

231
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:27,800
(Fang Hongsheng)

232
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:31,960
(Fang Hongsheng)
(Are they planning to let the auction fail?)

233
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:34,800
(Shen Gu)
(Mr. Fang makes all that money,)

234
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,879
(isn't it meant for doing some good?)

235
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,120
(Spend freely.)

236
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:41,360
- No need for that. I will do it myself.
- Alright.

237
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,360
Sorry

238
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:21,640
to keep you waiting.

239
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:26,120
You look stunning tonight.

240
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:28,760
Thank you.

241
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:32,760
The sapphire
matches your temperament well.

242
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:40,640
This was a gift from my grandfather
for my eighteenth birthday.

243
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:52,090
Your bow tie is crooked.

244
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:04,040
Thank you.

245
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:11,240
I have a gift for you.

246
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:15,040
Thank you for everything you have done

247
00:17:15,840 --> 00:17:17,560
for me and for Minghui.

248
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:19,960
Take a look.

249
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,800
Do you like it?

250
00:17:33,080 --> 00:17:34,640
Can you help me put it on?

251
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:37,760
Of course.

252
00:17:38,090 --> 00:17:43,020
♪The clouds hide the faint light
behind them♪

253
00:17:43,990 --> 00:17:48,120
♪A lonely bench on the street corner♪

254
00:17:48,460 --> 00:17:52,470
♪Where all feelings come to rest♪

255
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:57,859
♪In the night sky, the moon's trail♪

256
00:17:57,860 --> 00:18:01,849
♪Stitches up and soothes my sorrow♪

257
00:18:01,850 --> 00:18:04,729
♪The courage to get close to you♪

258
00:18:04,730 --> 00:18:08,360
♪Drives away my hesitation♪

259
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:11,720
It goes perfectly
with your necklace as well.

260
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,120
I really like it.

261
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,120
That is good.

262
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:18,379
♪You, in the album♪

263
00:18:18,380 --> 00:18:23,560
♪Shine through my past like starlight♪

264
00:18:24,050 --> 00:18:30,790
♪Starlight fills the sky above♪

265
00:18:56,800 --> 00:19:02,600
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

266
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:09,680
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

267
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:15,760
♪You turn and look back at me♪

268
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:22,400
♪In those same eyes
familiar tears quietly appear♪

269
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:28,880
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

270
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:35,640
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

271
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:42,080
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

272
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:49,040
♪Every dream I had became
something I want with you near♪

273
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:56,400
♪How many letters
have I written just for you♪

274
00:19:56,520 --> 00:20:02,200
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

275
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:09,239
♪From this life on no distance
could keep us apart♪

276
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:12,119
♪The promise we made♪

277
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:15,799
♪Will find its way
to be fulfilled one day♪

278
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:22,399
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

279
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:28,800
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

280
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:35,519
♪Can we still rewrite
the ending we face♪

281
00:20:35,520 --> 00:20:40,640
♪When regrets begin to turn around
you will hear it all♪

282
00:20:41,120 --> 00:20:44,120
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪

